data.description: Immaculate, well-maintained 4 bedroom, 3 bath, end unit condo, located in the prestigious gated community of the Villas at the International Club. The owners of this meticulously maintained home are the only ones who have lived in this condo since it was built.The condo was used as a second home for many years. Extremely spacious features include entering in the foyer with a breathtaking, vaulted cathedral ceilings, multiple tray ceilings and white plantation shutters throughout the house.  The kitchen has updated appliances, new backsplash, Corian countertops, plenty of cabinets, counter space and a pantry. Preparing dinner in the kitchen, entertaining in the dining room or living room you can enjoy the three sided fireplace. This is an extremely open floor plan with able outdoor space and plenty of natural light. With access to the large back porch from your living room and master bedroom you can enjoy the beautiful pond view with a lighted fountain at night. Enjoy year around with the three season windows. There is also an open deck off of the dining room with stairs to the yard.The covered front porch includes security, motion lighted stairs.The  master bedroom offers tray ceilings, a large walk-in closet, with access to the balcony. The master bath is very spacious and also features a Jetted tub, double vanities and walk in shower. The first floor also features 2 more spacious bedrooms one being a en suite.The Laundry room is on the first floor with plenty of storage space. Upstairs, one more bedroom with an en suite and a walk in closet. Across the hallway, "a loft area, great space for a cozy chair and a good book" is a bonus room being used as a family room. Looking for storage? There are two doors that lead to two large floored attic spaces for lots of storage. This condo is close to the villas pool which HOA has made it available for sunning & socializing year around. Stores, restaurants, the beach, golfing, boating are but minutes away. This would make a great second home or permanent residence. Close to Hospitals, shopping, and the Murrells Inlet Marshwalk, Huntington Beach State Park, and Brookgreen Gardens. Schedule a showing today!
